490
00:40:03,710 --> 00:40:05,470
Concentrate.

491
00:40:05,780 --> 00:40:07,496
You have to make a
good connection.

492
00:40:07,520 --> 00:40:09,620
You can't do that if
you're yapping your gums.

493
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:17,770
- You ready?
- Ready.

494
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:20,039
All right.

495
00:40:20,040 --> 00:40:22,110
See if we are drift compatible.

496
00:40:25,930 --> 00:40:28,110
Come on girls. Get it.

497
00:40:31,830 --> 00:40:34,170
Shoot. Come on.

498
00:40:36,610 --> 00:40:38,736
