- I'm scared.

515
00:41:50,070 --> 00:41:51,980
Baby. I'll catch you.
I promise. Come on.

516
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:55,170
- Come on, Amara.
- Jump.

517
00:42:01,090 --> 00:42:02,400
Take it off.

518
00:42:05,870 --> 00:42:07,250
