521
00:42:21,040 --> 00:42:22,340
I felt it too.

522
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:26,440
Jake, it's me. You there?

523
00:42:27,720 --> 00:42:28,980
Yeah, I'm here.

524
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:31,140
