- So it's gone.

534
00:43:02,380 --> 00:43:04,819
Gone is relative in
digital round mate.

535
00:43:04,820 --> 00:43:06,820
Running a modified
factorial algorithm

536
00:43:06,830 --> 00:43:09,240
I might be able to
reconstruct a few megabytes.

537
00:43:13,150 --> 00:43:14,500
There.

538
00:43:16,620 --> 00:43:18,130
