what happened.

552
00:44:23,060 --> 00:44:25,110
Neural connection terminated.

553
00:44:28,310 --> 00:44:30,870
Yeah, I guess they do.

554
00:44:36,360 --> 00:44:40,866
If you look at it sideways in
they maybe you can say that.

555
00:44:40,890 --> 00:44:43,270
Sorry, what are you...
What is going on here?

556
00:44:47,160 --> 00:44:48,560
48 is a...

557
00:44:50,200 --> 00:44:51,600
Get it done.

558
00:44:54,130 --> 00:44:55,580
Not a problem. Which...

559
00:44:58,000 --> 00:44:59,706
