What can I say? You
are right by mine.

580
00:46:30,690 --> 00:46:34,746
They are calling it Obsidian Fury.
He's never been a rogue like this.

581
00:46:34,770 --> 00:46:38,369
News feeds they are posting a
dozen Jaegers at the memorial.

582
00:46:38,370 --> 00:46:40,399
When I die, I want
that many send me off.

583
00:46:40,400 --> 00:46:43,429
Your pops gonna make you work
with boobs when you wash out.

584
