Jaegers do not show up
when the boob guy does.

585
00:46:45,240 --> 00:46:47,649
- Your dad works with boobs?
- He is a plastic surgeon.

586
00:46:47,650 --> 00:46:49,220
He does not just work with...

587
00:46:49,340 --> 00:46:51,866
I'm not gonna wash out.
I'm gonna be a pilot.

588
00:46:51,890 --> 00:46:55,720
Still, you die, man, they post
one Jaeger on your funeral.

589
00:46:56,310 --> 00:46:58,680
Maybe half a Jaeger.

590
00:46:58,870 --> 00:47:01,379
I heard this is where
they found Amara

591
00:47:01,380 --> 00:47:02,599
in half a Jaeger.

592
