Do you know where
I learned that?

600
00:47:39,560 --> 00:47:42,800
- On the street, you bitch...
- Ranger on deck.

601
00:47:45,610 --> 00:47:47,569
- She jumped me.
- She does not belong here.

602
00:47:47,570 --> 00:47:48,890
I don't care.

603
00:47:50,890 --> 00:47:54,480
When I first joined the
Corps, I was like you.

604
00:47:54,660 --> 00:47:57,760
Worse, I was nobody.

605
00:47:59,490 --> 00:48:05,436
But that woman we lay to rest today, Mako
Mori, she said, "Whoever you are..."

606
00:48:05,460 --> 00:48:08,660
